在過去幾十年觀察到的更暖的大氣溫度預計將導致更劇烈的水文循環，包括更極端的降雨事件。<ref>{{cite web|author=Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC)|year=1995|title=Second Assessment Synthesis of Scientific-Technical Information relevant to interpreting Article 2 of the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change|page=5|url=http://www.ipcc.ch/pdf/climate-changes-1995/2nd-assessment-synthesis.pdf|access-date=2017-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130309040926/http://www.ipcc.ch/pdf/climate-changes-1995/2nd-assessment-synthesis.pdf|archive-date=2013-03-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>由於氣候變化而發生的[海平面上升]]也大大增加了海岸侵蝕率。<ref>{{cite book|editor=Bicknell, Jane|display-editors=etal|title=Adapting Cities to Climate Change: Understanding and Addressing the Development Challenges|publisher=Earthscan|year=2009|isbn=978-1-84407-745-8|page=114|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=77Kmhw6sVOMC&pg=PA114|access-date=2017-01-30|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609042549/https://books.google.com/books?id=77Kmhw6sVOMC&pg=PA114|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>For an overview of other human activities that have increased coastal erosion rates, see: {{cite book|author=Goudie, Andrew|chapter=Accelerated coastal erosion|title=The Human Impact on the Natural Environment|publisher=MIT Press|year=2000|isbn=978-0-262-57138-8|page=311|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=r8l-DMj3XTgC&pg=PA311|access-date=2017-01-30|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609131930/https://books.google.com/books?id=r8l-DMj3XTgC&pg=PA311|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 全球環境影響 ==
